ass=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sumário","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <strong>elemento&nbsp;HTML <code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></strong> representa uma quebra temática entre elementos de nível de parágrafo (por exemplo , uma mudança da cena de uma história, ou uma mudança de tema com uma seção). Nas versões anteriores do HTML, representava uma linha horizontal. Pode continuar sendo exibida como uma linha horizontal nos navegadores, mas agora está definida em termos semânticos, em vez de termos de apresentação.</p>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Categorias de conteúdo</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Fluxo de conteúdo</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Conteúdo permitido</dfn> Nenhum, é um <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Empty_element\">empty element <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Omissão de Tag</dfn> Deve conter a tag de início, mas não precisa ter uma tag de encerramento.</li>\n <li><dfn>Elementos pai permitidos</dfn> Qualquer elemento que aceite <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">fluxo de conteúdo</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Interface DOM</dfn> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLHRElement\"><code>HTMLHRElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Este elemento inclui os </span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">atributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"align\"><a id=\"attr-align\" href=\"#attr-align\"><b><code>align</code></b></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"notecard inline deprecated\" title=\"\">Deprecated since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML4.01</a></span>&nbsp;<span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Obsolete since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Define a regra de alinhamento na página. Se nenhum valor for especificado, o valor padrão é <code>left</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"color\"><a id=\"attr-color\" href=\"#attr-color\"><b><code>color</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Denife a&nbsp;regra da cor através do nome da cor ou um valor hexadecimal.</dd>\n <dt id=\"noshade\"><a id=\"attr-noshade\" href=\"#attr-noshade\"><b><code>noshade</code></b></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"notecard inline deprecated\" title=\"\">Deprecated since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML4.01</a></span>&nbsp;<span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Obsolete since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Deine a regra para não ter sombreamento.</dd>\n <dt id=\"size\"><a id=\"attr-size\" href=\"#attr-size\"><b><code>size</code></b></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"notecard inline deprecated\" title=\"\">Deprecated since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML4.01</a></span>&nbsp;<span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Obsolete since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Denife a altura, em pixels.</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"notecard inline deprecated\" title=\"\">Deprecated since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML4.01</a></span>&nbsp;<span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Obsolete since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Define a regra de comprimento na página através de um valor em pixel ou porcentagem.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto. Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto.\n  Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto. Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>hr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto. Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto.\n  Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto. Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>O HTML acima irá produzir:</p>\n\n<p>Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto. Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto. Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto. Este é o primeiro parágrafo do texto.</p>\n\n<hr>\n<p>Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto. Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto. Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto. Este é o segundo parágrafo do texto.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Para alterar a aparencia da linha ou as lacunas entre ela e os parágrafos, utilize <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"CSS\">folhas de estilo em cascata</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/grouping-content.html#the-hr-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;hr&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Definição do elemento <code>hr</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/rendering.html#the-hr-element-0\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML Living Standard' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Sugestão de renderização padrão do elemento <code>hr</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/grouping-content.html#the-hr-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;hr&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/present/graphics.html#h-15.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;hr&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade nos Navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade